(2702, 1, '2023-10-28 18:29:33', '2023-10-28 23:29:33', '<p>H&amp;M’s Fashion Photoshoot Campaign is the Coolest Thing We’ve Seen</p>\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"align\":\"full\",\"mediaId\":2236,\"mediaLink\":\"https://demos.ascendoor.com/ascendoor-magazine-pro/hms-fashion-photoshoot-campaign/pexels-cottonbro-7870891-min/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":60,\"imageFill\":true,\"focalPoint\":{\"x\":\"0.97\",\"y\":\"0.37\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignfull is-stacked-on-mobile is-image-fill\" style=\"grid-template-columns:60% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\" style=\"background-image:url(https://demos.ascendoor.com/ascendoor-magazine-pro/wp-content/uploads/sites/57/2022/05/pexels-cottonbro-7870891-min.jpg);background-position:97% 37%\"><img src=\"https://demos.ascendoor.com/ascendoor-magazine-pro/wp-content/uploads/sites/57/2022/05/pexels-cottonbro-7870891-min.jpg\" alt=\"h&amp;m Fashion Week\" class=\"wp-image-2236 size-full\" /></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Now that spring is finally here, it\'s time to start transitioning your wardrobe from winter into the current season. That doesn\'t necessarily mean put away all sweaters and coats, because as we know spring can be very fickle. But there are a few tricks to making those winter-looks more spring friendly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Transitional Coats: Last week I talked about transitional coats, and these are the perfect items to add into your wardrobe right now. Lightweight, but will still keep you warm on a cool night.<br>Spring Sweaters: Layer with a transitional coat, or wear on its own, some of your winter sweaters are easy to wear into spring. I lived in these cashmere sweaters from Everlane all winter, and I know I\'ll be pairing them with skirts and shorts for spring.<br>Pumps instead of Boots: I\'ve traded in my boots for pumps. Keeping my feet warm isn\'t a priority anymore, so it\'s time to break out my favorite heels and pair back to effortless denim. These pumps have been worth the investment - I wear them the most during spring.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'H&amp;M’s Fashion Photoshoot Campaign', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2116-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-10-28 18:29:33', '2023-10-28 23:29:33', '', 2116, 'https://klutchproducts.com/?p=2702', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
