(2712, 1, '2023-10-28 18:29:34', '2023-10-28 23:29:34', 'The aughts were a bold time for eyewear. Stars were running around Hollywood in huge bug-eyed shades (very Paris Hilton) and clear, tinted square frames (very Eve), and I simply had to try them all. As a teen, I was completely obsessed with big, wraparound shield frames. (You could hide half of your face behind them—a shy teen’s dream!) I taped a 2006 Dior sunglasses ad starring Kate Moss, in which she wears huge black shield sunnies, onto my bedroom wall for inspiration. Britney Spears also rocked a pair of Dolce &amp; Gabbana shades, and I’ve been on the hunt for them ever since.', 'Bust Out Your 2000s Shield Shades', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2043-revision-v1', '', '', '2023-10-28 18:29:34', '2023-10-28 23:29:34', '', 2043, 'https://klutchproducts.com/?p=2712', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
